Author Functions
-----------------

1. New/Edit/Suggest Edits - Style/Content/Post/Data/Page




Data
-----

name - ui field for searching etc.
type - text   |   image
file - url of text (relative to ./data)    |  url of image(relative to ./images)
content - text/html content associated with the data (na if file != NULL)




Style
------

style of thumbnails




Content
--------

[type:"content", value:"[content,content,...]"]

[type:"data", style:"style_id", data:"data_id", id:"id", title:"title", info:"info", text:"text", style_text:""]

[type:"indirect", content:"content_id"]